author: @Yooniverse35
text:
Wow they were quite serious about this! It's nice to see since the members have actually ventured out in fashion and are doing really well for themselves. The professional model judges, the shield prize, they were not here to play! I feel like the girls' individual fashion styles / tastes were portrayed quite well and it had me actually rooting for the looks. KariSelle's creativity and playful nature to their outfits whilst still bringing attention to detail was worth noticing while on the other hand WinNing's classy approach and well-roundedness to their style was definitely more my taste! 
I'm quite upset this was only 2 episodes long lol but I understand that getting pros to be part of the show mustn't have been that easy. All in all, excellent job by the producers and ofc by AESPA 🖤🖤💜💜
